{"tid":89091,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下有無巴絲用iphone7成日hang機？","createTime":"2017-01-21T06:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T10:07:10.000Z","uid":12585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55e7d9975baac48c384b4b736ce22d80546ad899","tid":89091,"uid":12585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"我用緊iphone7+IOS10.0(未更新過，無亂咁下載廣告email等等<br />\n部機會間唔中hang機，事小就會hang幾分鐘郁唔到之後郁得翻，嚴重的就會hang到郁唔到要強制關機再開機咁。雖則話就普通事姐，可以強制關機就解決問題，但會成日都hang到咁真係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時有需要用嘅時候突然hang機真係好麻煩，啱先又強制關機完嚟<br />\n我見身邊朋友又好似未試過咁，可能係我唔知喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過落apple問(第一次以為部機壞咗，有信息反應但部機黑mon開唔到鎖)，佢話好正常好普遍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教我強制開機就送我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底得我係咁定點？係咪無解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebe7792e1a715b5e1383d58ff4c8c4f219f9d10","tid":89091,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"咁嘅問題聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似壞機"},{"pid":"4666030d3e7756abe603b8c688abe6dfcafcd118","tid":89091,"uid":12585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁嘅問題聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似壞機</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？拎去apple問，佢地好似唔太理我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01e94ad6814c48a0cb3f823671e76498e1fe5e6","tid":89091,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"我都係，幾次，試過開相機跟住hand死咗，退出唔到，㩒乜都冇用，最後只可以強制關機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br 